{"tid":683879,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"「Happy Birthday To Me」 岩布仙尼仲記得亞視","createTime":"2018-05-30T05:22:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-31T06:52:03.000Z","uid":54870,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0a386bd6b320e87926b0ea329b681736894c2160","tid":683879,"uid":54870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T05:22:28.000Z","msg":"昨日5月29日是意大利及AC米蘭名宿岩布仙尼41歲生日，不少人都有為他送上祝福，岩布仙尼亦在個人社交網頁發帖致謝。不過，岩布仙尼在Instagram和Facebook上載了自己與一對子女在生日蛋糕前的合照並寫下感謝所有人的生日祝福後，更hashtag了「happybirthdaytome」，相信他仍然記得香港的亞洲電視。<br />\n<br />\n各位若不善忘，應該仍然記得2004年5月29日的亞視台慶，亞視找來當時正訪港的AC米蘭出席，同日生日的岩布仙尼除了要看聽不明白的節目，更被主持朱慧珊要求唱生日歌，結果岩布仙尼無奈哼出「Happy Birthday To Me」，此片段更在網上不斷播放。<br />\n今年岩布仙尼生日，除了不少球迷在其社交網頁留言送祝福，亦有估計是香港的球迷祝岩布仙尼和ATV生日快樂，另外，香港足球評述員陳祉俊亦在Facebook轉發了岩布仙尼的Ig post，並以【亞視嚟嘅？！】為題，表示「岩布仙尼又生日喇！睇佢 instagram 個 hashtag，就知亞視對佢影響幾深&hellip;&hellip;」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tL3qhZQJk7E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DtL3qhZQJk7E&d=bJKBWPzbAlOPooFAOkuCoB4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=b06ac79a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tL3qhZQJk7E</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/BjX7mqgByWn/?taken-by=massimoambrosini\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FBjX7mqgByWn%2F%3Ftaken-by%3Dmassimoambrosini&d=bJKBWPzbAlOPooFAOkuCoB4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=e365264b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FBjX7mqgByWn%2F%3Ftaken-by%3Dmassimoambrosini&h=40604b2c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/BjX7mqgByWn/?taken-by=massimoambrosini</a>"},{"pid":"f4197829f0b5b25aa2912c7cdbe42c3beff6dc57","tid":683879,"uid":54870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T05:32:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20180530/58254827?_ga=2.173001955.1185588804.1527472511-1347733541.1527472511\" data-sr-url=\"h